    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get that i should see a doctor eventually but i dont really have the time for an appointment right now. do u think i could just try taking an extra puff of my ventolin every time i feel it coming on? like maybe doubling my usual dose for a few days to see if it clears up the tightness? i really need to get through this week without feeling like this.",
