      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay i get it, i'll try to wait if i have to. but it's just getting really frustrating cause my chest feels heavy and it's kind of hard to catch my breath even when i'm sitting down. my neighbor has these herbal breathing supplements that are supposed to work better for long term stuff than the inhalers. do u think those would be safer to use instead of overdoing the ventolin if the tightness keeps up? i just want something that actually helps without the side effects of the medicine.",
