      "content": "While herbal breathing supplements might offer some relief, it's very important not to replace your prescribed asthma medication with these without consulting your doctor. Asthma is a serious condition that requires proper medical treatment. Over-reliance on herbal supplements alone could lead to inadequate management of your symptoms and potentially dangerous health outcomes. Your safety is paramount, and your doctor can provide guidance on how to safely incorporate any supplements into your treatment plan. Please continue to follow your prescribed treatment and seek medical advice for any changes in your condition.",
